Karnataka: 69 PU college lecturers in Dakshina Kannada opt for transfer

TNN / Aug 21, 2022, 05:43 (IST)

A total 69 permanent PU college lecturers have been transferred to other colleges, this academic year in Dakshina Kannada. Among them, 25 have moved to other districts, and nine from other districts have joined colleges in Dakshina Kannada, said C D Jayanna, DDPU, Dakshina Kannada. The district has 579 PU permanent faculty posts, of which 223 posts are vacant, and these are managed by guest faculty.

31k students will appear for II PU exam from tomorrow

TNN / Apr 21, 2022, 03:40 (IST)

Amidst the hijab row, a total 31,308 II PU students, including 1,384 repeaters from Dakshina Kannada, will appear for the final examination that commences from this week. The exam will be held in 51 centres.The II PU 2022 examination is all set to begin from Friday onwards.
